<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>About Us </title>

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 15px 0;
        }

        .navbar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .navbar .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .navbar nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
        }

        .navbar nav ul li {
            margin: 0 15px;
        }

        .navbar nav ul li a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .hero {
            background-image: url('/images/LuxuryHotel.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            padding: 100px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            color: #fff;
            text-shadow: black 1px 0 8px;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #fff;
            text-shadow: black 1px 0 10px;
        }

        .about {
            padding: 50px 0;
            background-color: #fff;
        }

        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .about-text {
            flex: 1;
            margin-right: 20px;
        }

        .about-text h2 {
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .about-text p {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .about-image {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .about-image img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .scrolling-text {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 15px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .scrolling-text marquee {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .mission-vision {
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            padding: 50px 0;
        }

        .mission-vision .section-title h2 {
            font-size: 36px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .mission, .vision {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .mission h3, .vision h3 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .group-section {
            padding: 50px 0;
            background-color: #fff;
        }

        .group-section .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .group-section .section-title h2 {
            font-size: 36px;
        }

        .group-list {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .hotel-item {
            width: 30%;
            margin: 15px 0;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .hotel-item img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .hotel-item h3 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .hotel-item p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #777;
        }

        .image-scrolling {
            display: flex;
            overflow-x: scroll;
            padding: 30px 0;
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
        }

        .image-scrolling img {
            width: 300px;
            height: 200px;
            margin-right: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .image-scrolling img:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        footer .social-icons {
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        footer .social-icons a {
            color: #fff;
            margin: 0 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        footer .social-icons a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="navbar">
            <div class="logo">EliteEscapes</div>
            <nav>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/about">About Us</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">Services</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="scrolling-text">
        <marquee behavior="scroll" direction="left">Welcome to our prestigious EliteEscapes - Offering luxurious stays across the globe!</marquee>
    </section>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>EliteEscapes</h1>
            <p>Offering Luxury and Comfort Across Multiple Destinations</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="about-text">
                <h2>Welcome to Our Group of Hotels</h2>
                <p>We are a distinguished group of hotels that have redefined the hospitality industry with a rich portfolio of premium hotels around the world. Our collection includes a range of properties designed to cater to the varying needs of our discerning guests, from luxury resorts to business-friendly hotels.</p>
                <p>Our mission is to provide exceptional experiences, personalized services, and world-class facilities to ensure each guest has a memorable stay, wherever they choose to visit.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="about-image">
                <img src="/images/LuxuryHotel.jpg" alt="EliteEscapes">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="group-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-title">
                <h2>Our Hotels</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="group-list">
                <div class="hotel-item">
                    <img src="/images/hotel1.jpg">
                    <h3>Hotel Luxe</h3>
                    <p>A five-star luxury hotel in the heart of Paris, offering unparalleled comfort and elegance.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="hotel-item">
                    <img src="/images/hotel2.jpg" alt="Hotel 2">
                    <h3>Resort Bliss</h3>
                    <p>A beachfront paradise in the Maldives, designed for relaxation and indulgence.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="hotel-item">
                    <img src="/images/hotel3.jpg" alt="Hotel 3">
                    <h3>City Heights</h3>
                    <p>A modern business hotel in New York, providing the perfect space for professionals.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    
    <footer>
        <div class="footer-content">
            <p>&copy; All Rights Reserved</p>
            <div class="social-icons">
                <a href="#">Facebook</a>
                <a href="#">Instagram</a>
                <a href="#">LinkedIn</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
